Package nl.idgis.geoide.util.streams

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    StreamProcessor
    The StreamProcessor interface provides generic utilities to work with reactive streams.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AkkaStreamProcessor
    An StreamProcessor implementation that uses an Akka actor system for scheduling.
    AkkaStreamProcessor.ConsumeByteStringsActor
    An actor that consumes bytes from a publisher of type ByteString and sends the bytes to the caller.
    AkkaStreamProcessor.InputStreamPublishActor
    An Akka actor that publishes an InputStream as a stream of ByteStrings of configurable length.
    AkkaStreamProcessor.InputStreamSubscription
    Reactive streams subscription for input streams.
    SingleValuePublisher<T>
    A publisher implementation that immediately produces a single preset value to each subscription.
